WEBVTT

00:01:28.434 --> 00:01:32.247
It doesn't actually take pictures,
but it's a hell of a lot cheaper,

00:01:32.271 --> 00:01:34.232
and you still feel like you were there.

00:01:34.256 --> 00:01:36.581
(Laughter)

00:01:36.605 --> 00:01:37.873
(Clears his throat)

00:01:37.897 --> 00:01:42.717
(Laughter)

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.445
"Dear Sir, good day,
compliments of the day,

00:01:48.469 --> 00:01:50.277
and my best wishes to you and family.

00:01:50.690 --> 00:01:51.761
(Breathes in)

00:01:51.785 --> 00:01:54.094
I know this letter
will come to you surprisingly,

00:01:54.118 --> 00:01:56.344
but let it not be a surprise to you,

00:01:56.368 --> 00:01:59.304
for nature has a way
of arriving unannounced,

00:01:59.328 --> 00:02:01.929
and, as an adage says,
originals are very hard to find,